text: I am proud of being among the select audience when you were rechristened Bakait.. Bhai tujhse baat  karne me alag hi maza aata hai. text: Most of our discussions were related how to do the bare minimum to get good marks in an assigment (cc Nishith and subhajit sir). text: Whatever limite conversations we had, it was always amazing. Loved meeting you and gradually getting to know more about you. You are an awesome person and insanely sweet. Wo DS ka red black trees ka assignment hamesha yaad rahega. Stay the same and stay in touch.

text:

text: Teraa bahot RR suna hai pure 3-4 saal. Jab tere room aayo ya to tu so rha hota tha ya laptop ke saamne rota tha. One of the most intelligent people I know. I still feel terko apni dukaan ke liye website bana leni chahiye the. Aur kya hi maanga tha teri family ne tujhse. Also do great things in the field of systems. love your passion about it.

text: Bhai. I had great fun talking to you about everything. Tu jis high level pe sochta hai assignment mein questions wo dekhke merko bahot stupid feel hota hai. text: Dost max pro. First time baat hi shayad Psychology me hui this. Kya weirdcourse tha wo. Uske baad networks aur fir placement. Placement ke waqt toh tune hi depression see bachaya tha. text: You were my constant partner at the front seat at Rm101.. even in those almost empty compilers and toc lectures. text:
First memory of you I remember is you asking to  Rajat sir, "Why is this thing (an equation on board) non trivial". From then having you as a friend, working with you on all the projects (damn david didn't send us the money :( ), and getting to know you have all been a pleasure. You inspire me to try new things in life, and not procastinating. Your passion and ambition about things is unparalleled and I wish I could have some amount that. 

Also all the best for the novel. I cant wait to have that on my shelf.  Keep working your ass off to write more amazing stuff
author: Keshav  Bansal

text:
I dont think we would have ever met if not for snehal. From sucking in ICPC 2 times in a row, not getting money for the nutanix hackathon, to almost all assignments and projects together. I don't think I will feel more lucky than this to have met someone. If not for you, I am pretty sure I could have completed any project. And Best is your ability to threaten people to work.. and those gpu grabbing skills 

I would always want you in my team if I am working on a project.. and more so like one oof my bestestt friends.. Though our friendship depends on how much I like the drama suggestion you gave..

Earn load of money in korea.. send me samung watches, kindles, airpods

From winning the nutanix hackathon to our first paper and literally having the same resume.. its been an awesome experience. All the best

PS: who is the girl behind you in this dp?

text: Kya se kya ho gye dekhte dekhte. Itna evolution toh kisi ka nhi dekha. First year me toh baat nhi hui kyoki tum chemistry ke the :D. Tera passion dekhke bahot accha lagta. Awesome personality. text: Always will be uncle for me.. cant even think of calling you anything else. Mess table conversations were always so fun with you. text:
